CPU09BP(10+4)

Provides:
* DIN41612 female connectors, up to 14 slots
* 10 slots UniFLEX
* 3 slots CPU09IOP or 4 slots FLEX
* ATX power connector
* on board extra fuse
* connection for power on/off
* connection for /reset
* Multiple ground and 5V power pins for optimal operation
* provisions for running special voltages and signals over the backplane
* fits in a 19" 3U rack
 